title: Google drive has my backed up messages from my 3xl. It will not download to my pixel 5!
content: I'm soooo frustrated.  I have all my texts backed up on my Google drive under pixel 3xl.  I cannot get them to my new pixel 5.  I cannot do a phone transfer.  I tried the stupid 3rd party app.  I've factory reset it 2 times.  I select 3xl to back up and it says unsuccessful.  What else can be done?
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 5
